==Mandarin==
===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī jŭ lĭang dé

==Japanese==
===Pronunciation===
[[Hiragana]]: いっきょりょうとく
[[Romaji]]: ikkyo-ryōtoku

===Etymology===
Literally: One action, two gains.

===Idiom===
'''[[一]][[舉]][[兩]][[得]]''' ([[Traditional Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') [[kill two birds with one stone]]; do one task and finish two or more goals.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[举]][[两]][[得]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

[[一]][[挙]][[両]][[得]] ([[Japanese]])

